        <UserObject label="" mermaidData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;flowchart TD\n    %% === Clients ===\n    WebApp[Web App] --&gt; API[API Layer]\n    MobileApp[Mobile App] --&gt; API\n    CLI[CLI] --&gt; API\n    BatchJob[Batch Job] --&gt; API\n\n    %% === API Layer ===\n    API --&gt; HTTPServer[HTTP Server]\n    API --&gt; Validation[Request Validation]\n    API --&gt; FileUpload[File Upload Handler]\n    API --&gt; Routes[API Endpoints]\n\n    %% === Endpoints ===\n    Routes --&gt; ExtractText[extract_text]\n    Routes --&gt; ExtractInfo[extract_info]\n    Routes --&gt; ExtractImages[extract_images]\n    Routes --&gt; ExtractTables[extract_tables]\n    Routes --&gt; RenderScreenshot[render_screenshot]\n\n    %% === Optional Async Queue ===\n    API --&gt; AsyncQueue[Queue Worker]\n    AsyncQueue --&gt; Service[PDF Parsing Service]\n\n    %% === Sync Path ===\n    API --&gt; Service\n\n    %% === Service Layer ===\n    Service --&gt; GetText[getText]\n    Service --&gt; GetInfo[getInfo]\n    Service --&gt; GetImage[getImage]\n    Service --&gt; GetTable[getTable]\n    Service --&gt; GetScreenshot[getScreenshot]\n\n    %% === Response ===\n    Service --&gt; Response[Response JSON]\n&quot;&#xa;}" id="Etss8OlZKyy1OCD3e9IM-1">
